Hello and welcome to the cubemoji server, run by <@170358606590377984>. This server is a hub for cubemoji bot updates as well as to provide any feedback or questions on the bot.

**Rules**
- Keep things on topic. Please keep discussions limited to cubemoji or emojis as this server isn't really meant as a general discussion server.
- No NSFW content. The opt-in best-of channel shows cubemoji content from across the servers its on and may be NSFW from time to time.
- No harassment. This includes insulting other members, using slurs, hate speech, targeted harassment, etc.
- No advertising or spam is allowed.
- Follow Discord Community Guidelines https://discord.com/guidelines as well as TOS https://discord.com/terms

**etc**
- Please report any moderation concerns by pinging or DMing  <@170358606590377984>. If you would like cubemoji on your server, you can also DM him.
